; Regression test for issue #2019:
; Account names with embedded spaces in automated transaction predicates
; should not require quoting.  The unquoted form "= income:b c" should
; be treated as a single pattern matching the account "income:b c",
; equivalent to "= 'income:b c'".

account liabilities:a
account income:b c

= income:b c
    liabilities:a  -1
    equity:adjustments  1

2021/03/18 * test
    income:b c  $1.00
    equity:adjustments

test bal
               $1.00  income:b c
              $-1.00  liabilities:a
--------------------
                   0
end test
